CVS modules needed by AutoSite
------------------------------
AutoSite
logview_sql
menumaker
sitebuilder


Database setup from scratch for Mysql
-------------------------------------
A. LogView SQL: 1. Edit the file logview_sql/LogViewSQL.pmod/config.h
                2. Change the definition of "DATABASE" to the correct value.
                3. Run logview_sql/tools/setup.pike


